data.title: Time Warner (A)
data.meta_description: Time Warner (a) - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Time Warner is a global media and entertainment company with businesses in television networks, filmed entertainment, publishing and interactive services. It uses its industry-leading scale and popular brands like HBO, Warner Bros., and Turner Broadcasting to create and deliver high-quality content across multiple platforms worldwide. Time Warner has a long history of acquisitions and mergers, including forming AOL Time Warner through the merger with AOL in 2000 in what was then the largest merger in business history. The company continues to innovate and adapt its businesses to changing industry trends and consumer behaviors.
